items.sentence: Tom isn't waiting for you. He's waiting for me.
Tom was able to talk Mary out of marrying John.
Tom was able to figure out how to open the box.
Tom was aware that Mary had moved to Australia.
Tom was the only boy that Mary saw in the park.
Tom was the only person Mary needed to talk to.
Tom was the only one who wasn't at the meeting.
I'm here to help Tom, not the other way around.
Tom was with Mary the last time she visited us.
Tom was the first one to encourage me to do so.
